                h5.trackDescription(style='font-family:Verdana; font-size: ') The Chest X-Ray Essentials track is a quintessential in-depth review of X-ray radiological anatomy, physiology and pathology. It is intended to provide core competency in this essential skillset.
              p.lead(style='font-size:40px')
                h4.trackLearn(style='font-family:Georgia') WHAT YOU'LL LEARN
              ul(style='font-family:Georgia; font-size: 14px')
